name: Mr & Mrs Signs & Photo Prop
description:
Hand painted Mr & Mrs signs with ribbon motif and matching white vintage frames. Hang from ceremony signing chairs with white ribbon or use as a cute photo prop for the new couple.  
Also available as Bride & Groom, personalized names and as a Thank You sign set, perfect for a cute photo shoot to add a personalized touch to your thank you cards. 

Each sign is hand painted to order and sealed with a matte varnish.

♥ Measurements vary depending on vintage frame sets however most are approx. 25 x 20 cm, contact me to view selection of frames.
♥ Have something different in mind? Custom orders are always welcome, e-mail me at nyssaskorji@hotmail.com for prices and possibilities. x

name: Ceremony / Reception Signage
description:
These hand painted ceremony and reception signs add the perfect touch to your wedding or event to let your guests know exactly where you are. 
As each sign is painted to order the ribbon motif and wording can be changed to suit your event. 

♥ Measurements (45 x 60 cm) 
♥ Have something different in mind? Custom orders are always welcome, e-mail me at nyssaskorji@hotmail.com for prices and possibilities. x

name: Bonbonniere Pouches x 100
description:
This listing is for 100 handmade bonbonniere pouches, measuring 10 x 5.5cm. (Thank you tags not included)
 Each pouch is made to order with the fabric of your choice, and is closed with either jute or bakers twine. 
Each pouch is individually stamped with 70mm lettering and heart, both available in a range of colors.

These little bags are perfect for adding a personalized touch to your upcoming wedding or event, and can easily be filled with boiled candy, flowers seeds, or gift of your choice. 

♥ Measurements (10 x 5.5 cm)
♥ Please allow up to 2 weeks for your order to be completed, I’ll be in contact to finalize fabric and stamp choices.
♥ Have something different in mind? Custom orders are always welcome, e-mail me at nyssaskorji@hotmail.com for price, smaller numbers and possibilities. x

name: Book Art
description:
This listing is for 10 custom made book sculptures.

Each sculpture is hand folded from a up-cycled paperback novel, allowing for a vast range of shapes and sizes.
E-mail me with your choice of design, and preferred sizing i.e : diamond, lantern, triangle,  flat or cylindrical. Sculptures look great as an addition to a book shelf, table center piece and can easily be hung with the addition of fisherman's wire. 

♥ All sets will be appropriately packaged and posted to ensure safe delivery.
